## 2. Monetization Lane Agents (Billing / Pricing)

### `tm.billing.record_usage`

- Purpose: Convert a Middleman usage event into a billing‑grade record (Stripe, internal ledger, etc.). This reflects how usage‑based billing systems record discrete consumption events. [stripe](https://stripe.com/resources/more/usage-based-pricing-for-saas-how-to-make-the-most-of-this-pricing-model)

```json
{
  "name": "tm.billing.record_usage",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Record a usage event for billing in Stripe or the internal ledger.",
  "input_schema": {
    "type": "object",
    "required": [
      "tenant_id",
      "model_id",
      "units",
      "unit_type",
      "trace_id",
      "occurred_at"
    ],
    "properties": {
      "tenant_id": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "Tenant linked to this usage."
      },
      "model_id": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "Tap919 model ID that generated usage."
      },
      "units": {
        "type": "number",
        "description": "Quantity consumed (e.g., 1 task, 1.234 units of 1k tokens)."
      },
      "unit_type": {
        "type": "string",
        "enum": ["per_call", "per_task", "per_1k_tokens"],
        "description": "Billing unit for this usage."
      },
      "trace_id": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "Correlation/trace ID from Middleman telemetry."
      },
      "occurred_at": {
        "type": "string",
        "format": "date-time",
        "description": "Timestamp of when the usage occurred (UTC)."
      },
      "cost_estimate": {
        "type": "number",
        "description": "Estimated cost at time of event (pre‑discounts)."
      },
      "metadata": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Any additional metadata (provider, tokens, lane).",
        "additionalProperties": true
      }
    }
  },
  "output_schema": {
    "type": "object",
    "required": ["status"],
    "properties": {
      "status": {
        "type": "string",
        "enum": ["recorded", "skipped", "error"],
        "description": "Result of the recording operation."
      },
      "external_usage_id": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "External billing system usage ID (e.g., Stripe usage record ID)."
      },
      "error": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "Error message if status is 'error'."
      }
    }
  }
}
```

